Package com.pandora.controllers.requestbodies.services

Class CellCalculationRequestServiceImpl

java.lang.Object
com.pandora.controllers.requestbodies.services.CellCalculationRequestServiceImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
CellCalculationRequestService
@Service public class CellCalculationRequestServiceImpl extends Object implements CellCalculationRequestService
The CellCalculationRequestServiceImpl class implements the CellCalculationRequestService interface. It is a service responsible for preprocessing and processing cell calculation requests. It is annotated with Service. It utilizes various services for managing Y values, discharges, volumes, upstream sources, terrestrial sources, local date-time operations, and cell timestep calculations.
Version:
0.0.1
Author:
Wim Joost van Hoek
